Webp 

For an academic and detailed exploration of arithmetic coding used in image compression technologies such as WebP, sources like Howard, P. G., & Vitter, J. S. (1992). Arithmetic coding for data compression. Proceedings of the IEEE, 82(6), 857-865 and Sayood, K. (2017). Introduction to data compression (5th ed.). Morgan Kaufmann Publishers would provide comprehensive insights. These works outline the theoretical and practical aspects of arithmetic coding, emphasizing its application in various compression standards, including those used in modern image compression methodologies.

