Taubman, D., & Marcellin, M. W. (2002). "JPEG2000: Image Compression Fundamentals, Standards, and Practice". Journal of Electronic Imaging. This book, while focused on JPEG2000, provides essential background on image compression technologies that might contrast with WebP's approach.

