Miano, J. (1999). Compressed Image File Formats: JPEG, PNG, GIF, XBM, BMP. Addison-Wesley Professional. [Discusses various compression schemes within the context of TIFF and other image formats.]


Welch, T. A. (1984). A Technique for High-Performance Data Compression. IEEE Computer, 17(6), 8-19. This seminal paper introduces the LZW algorithm, detailing its mechanisms and applications in data compression.
Murray, J. D., & vanRyper, W. (1996). Encyclopedia of Graphics File Formats. Sebastopol, CA: O'Reilly & Associates. This book provides comprehensive coverage on various graphics formats, including TIFF, and discusses their respective compression techniques such as LZW.


